      <div class="case-summary">
        <h2>Description</h2>
        <p>The mobile banking sector has been growing extensively over the past years creating opportunities for people to bring together all their finances into one place. Together with renowned mobile banking companies we designed flexbible insurances the customer could sign up for (and cancel) in three simple steps. This was made possible by developing a secure API connection with our partners.
        The customer clicks on the insurance option, sees the terms and conditions and signs up. The customer is less likely to step out during the registration process because of the many details they would normally have to fill out and added benefit is that the customer has an overview of all his finances in one app.</p>
      </div>
